    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >梦想过拥有并经营自己的洗衣店吗？现在您可以在 “自助洗衣店模拟器 ”中实现这一梦想！从一家店铺开始，扩展到许多不同的独特地点。迎接挑战，建立你的被动收入帝国！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169070/extras/c70648d28479368001556fd51a89d587.avif?t=1730351683\" width=250 height=75 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169070/extras/19610647319cc2ed89b06dd9ff248e9d.poster.avif?t=1730351683\" width=406 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169070/extras/19610647319cc2ed89b06dd9ff248e9d.webm?t=1730351683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169070/extras/19610647319cc2ed89b06dd9ff248e9d.mp4?t=1730351683\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用独特的家具、鲜艳的色彩和高效的布局来定制您的自助洗衣店。打造一个能不断吸引顾客的诱人空间。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169070/extras/ebd986e18028298b46a5e91f20ef5839.avif?t=1730351683\" width=250 height=75 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169070/extras/127b7c43e43340139ce35d0b1619264d.poster.avif?t=1730351683\" width=406 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169070/extras/127b7c43e43340139ce35d0b1619264d.webm?t=1730351683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169070/extras/127b7c43e43340139ce35d0b1619264d.mp4?t=1730351683\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过从机器上收集硬币、跟踪每日收入和明智地进行再投资来管理你的收入。最大化你的收入，看着你的利润增长。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169070/extras/4bb83b61262c28b90953cd2891ce9054.avif?t=1730351683\" width=250 height=75 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169070/extras/dabc71481fde38c21114d7c9ffad2cc5.poster.avif?t=1730351683\" width=406 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169070/extras/dabc71481fde38c21114d7c9ffad2cc5.webm?t=1730351683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169070/extras/dabc71481fde38c21114d7c9ffad2cc5.mp4?t=1730351683\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >保持店内一尘不染，吸引更多顾客。一个干净整洁、井井有条的自助洗衣店能确保顾客满意并再次光顾。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169070/extras/610350027b7f49840588912453f7b237.avif?t=1730351683\" width=250 height=75 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169070/extras/afd0fea6240e3bba0ced5488683a65de.poster.avif?t=1730351683\" width=406 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169070/extras/afd0fea6240e3bba0ced5488683a65de.webm?t=1730351683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3169070/extras/afd0fea6240e3bba0ced5488683a65de.mp4?t=1730351683\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >逐步开设新店，升级设备，提供更多服务。循序渐进地发展自助洗衣店业务，适应顾客需求，提高店铺评级。</p>",
